    "## Ethics and data use\n",
    "\n",
    "- This project uses a **public, anonymised** credit dataset (no names, addresses, or direct identifiers).\n",
    "- The `ID` column is treated as a technical identifier only and is **excluded from modelling**.\n",
    "- The work focuses on methodological evaluation of ML models and an agentic decision workflow, not on real-world lending decisions for identifiable individuals.\n"
   ]
  },
