    "On average:\n",
    "Balances are decreasing slightly over time.\n",
    "\n",
    "Large variance suggests:\n",
    "\n",
    "Some customers:\n",
    "\n",
    "* Increasing debt rapidly (positive slope)\n",
    "* Decreasing debt rapidly (negative slope)\n",
    "\n",
    "Trend features help detect early warning signals.\n",
    "\n",
    "# Overall Interpretation\n",
    "\n",
    "Your engineered dataset now captures:\n",
    "\n",
    "1️⃣ Level of risk (delays)\n",
